These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, singing, board-games, video-games
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, sailing, golf, basketball
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is between the person who's sport is golf and the person who's sport is sailing##2
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
3. the person who's sport is golf is not to the left of the person who's sport is golf##8
4. the person who's sport is sailing is not the person who's hobby is board-games##6
5. the person who's hobby is board-games is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is photography##5
6. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Hobby   | video-games  | photography | board-games | singing  |
| Sport   | badminton | golf   | basketball  | sailing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-2::.
There 4 different types of food: potato, cucumber, lemon, blueberry
The people have 4 different jobs:  manager, pilot, musician, security-guard
1. the security-guard is not to the left of the security-guard##8
2. the person eating potato is somewhere to the right of the person eating blueberry##5
3. the person eating potato is the pilot##1
4. the person eating blueberry is between the person eating potato and the person eating cucumber##2
5. the person eating cucumber is somewhere between the person eating lemon and the manager##7
6. the musician is somewhere to the left of the person eating cucumber##5
7. the manager is not to the left of the manager##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |        2        |    3     |     4      |
| Food   | lemon | cucumber          | blueberry | potato     |
| Job    | musician      | security-guard | manager | pilot |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-3::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  manager, project-manager, doctor, teacher
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, documentary, zombie, romance
1. the person watching fantasy movies is not to the left of the doctor##8
2. the person watching documentary movies is on the far left##1
3. the project-manager is on the right of the manager##1
4. the project-manager is in an even position##4
5. the teacher is on the far left or far right##3
6. the manager is somewhere to the left of the person watching romance movies##5
7. the teacher is the person watching zombie movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Job           | manager | project-manager | doctor     | teacher |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary    | romance   | fantasy | zombie    |

