.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-4::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, hip-hop, d&b, dubstep
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: water-polo, swimming, badminton, ice-hockey
1. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
2. the person who's sport is water-polo is not to the left of the person who's sport is swimming##8
3. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
4. the fan of dubstep is not to the right of the person who's sport is badminton##8
5. the fan of pop is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
6. the fan of pop is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
7. the fan of d&b is somewhere to the left of the fan of dubstep##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |   3    |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | d&b   | hip-hop         | dubstep   | pop    |
| Sport         | swimming | ice-hockey | badminton | water-polo |

