.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-5::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, crime, time-travel, action
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, snowboarding, tennis, biathlon
1. the person watching action movies is somewhere between the person watching mystery movies and the person watching crime movies##7
2. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is tennis##5
3. the person watching action movies is somewhere between the person watching time-travel movies and the person watching mystery movies##7
4. the person watching time-travel movies is not to the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##8
5. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere between the person watching crime movies and the person who's sport is snowboarding##7
6. the person who's sport is snowboarding is somewhere to the right of the person watching action movies##5
7. the person who's sport is snowboarding is not to the left of the person watching mystery movies##8
8. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left or right of the person watching action movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | crime   | time-travel | action | mystery    |
| Sport         | rowing | biathlon   | tennis   | snowboarding |

