2. the fan of electronic is somewhere to the left of the person eating carrot##5
3. the person eating orange is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
4. the fan of hip-hop is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3
5. the person eating carrot is somewhere to the left of the person eating pepper##5
6. the person eating apricot is not to the left of the fan of electronic##8
7. the person eating apricot is the fan of electronic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3   |    4    |
