.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, tea, 7up, lemonade
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, weightlifting, climbing, swimming
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is not to the left of the person drinking tea##8
2. the person who's sport is swimming is somewhere between the person drinking lemonade and the person who's sport is climbing##7
3. the person who's sport is climbing is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is parkour##5
4. the person who's sport is swimming is not to the left of the person who's sport is parkour##8
5. the person who's sport is swimming is not to the left of the person drinking tea##8
6. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
7. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
8. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |   2    |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage   | tea      | 7up | coffee | lemonade   |
| Sport      | parkour | climbing | swimming  | weightlifting |

