2. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is cricket##5
3. the software-developer is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
4. the person who's sport is cricket is somewhere between the person who's sport is surfing and the software-developer##7
5. the nurse is not to the right of the scientist##8
6. the scientist is somewhere between the person who's sport is surfing and the nurse##7

.:: Answer ::.
