.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-12::.
There 4 different types of food: strawberry, eggplant, cauliflower, garlic
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, drawing, traveling, fishing
1. the person eating cauliflower is not to the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##8
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is not to the right of the person eating eggplant##8
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is somewhere to the right of the person eating garlic##5
4. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person eating cauliflower is between the person who's hobby is fishing and the person who's hobby is traveling##2
6. the person eating eggplant is on the far left##1
7. the person eating cauliflower is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is fishing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Food    | eggplant        | garlic | cauliflower      | strawberry    |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks | traveling   | drawing | fishing |

