.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, almond-milk, 7up, milk
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, sailing, snowboarding, badminton
1. the person who's sport is badminton is not to the right of the person who's sport is baseball##8
2. the person who's sport is badminton is not to the right of the person drinking tea##8
3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
4. the person drinking tea is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person drinking milk is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's sport is baseball is somewhere between the person who's sport is snowboarding and the person drinking almond-milk##7
7. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
8. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | milk | almond-milk         | 7up    | tea       |
| Sport      | sailing | badminton | baseball | snowboarding |

