2. the person drinking coffee is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is somewhere to the right of the person drinking coffee##5
4. the person drinking fanta is between the person drinking coffee and the person who's hobby is video-games##2
5. the person drinking water is on the far left##1
6. the person who's hobby is singing is between the person who's hobby is puzzles and the person who's hobby is board-games##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2      |     3      |      4       |
