.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-18::.
There 4 different types of food: corn, cranberry, apple, onion
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, sudoku, puzzles, skydiving
1. the person eating apple is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
2. the person eating apple is not to the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##8
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the person eating onion##1
5. the person eating onion is on the left of the person eating cranberry##1
6. the person eating cranberry is between the person who's hobby is sudoku and the person eating onion##2
7. the person eating apple is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Food    | onion        | cranberry | corn | apple |
| Hobby   | skydiving | puzzles | sudoku   | board-games    |

