.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-19::.
4 different pets are kept: horse, dog, lizard, chinchilla
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, helicopter, motorbike, quad-bike
1. the owner of the chinchilla is not the person driving the motorbike##6
2. the person driving the motorbike is not to the right of the owner of the lizard##8
3. the owner of the dog is somewhere between the owner of the lizard and the owner of the chinchilla##7
4. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere to the right of the owner of the horse##5
5. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere to the left of the person driving the quad-bike##5
6. the person driving the airplane is not to the right of the person driving the helicopter##8
7. the owner of the dog is not to the left of the person driving the quad-bike##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |   3   |    4    |
| Pet         | horse  | chinchilla | dog  | lizard  |
| Transport   | airplane | helicopter   | quad-bike | motorbike |

