.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-20::.
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, bird, snake, lizard
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, quad-bike, tram, ship
1. the person driving the quad-bike is not the owner of the rabbit##6
2. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
3. the owner of the lizard is not to the left of the person driving the ship##8
4. the owner of the snake is the person driving the trike##1
5. the owner of the lizard is somewhere between the person driving the quad-bike and the person driving the trike##7
6. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
7. the person driving the tram is between the person driving the ship and the owner of the snake##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Pet         | bird    | lizard | rabbit | snake |
| Transport   | quad-bike | ship      | tram     | trike     |

 